scene.message:
Nanjo: Sonomura's mother, of{nl}
all places, works at a{nl}
company like that?!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ah! Dang it! Maybe I{nl}
should've brought flowers or{nl}
something. Oh well, can't be{nl}
helped!{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: You're all Maki's{nl}
friends? Oh, I'm so glad.{waitkey}She's been in and out of the{nl}
hospital ever since she was{nl}
a child, you know?{waitkey}I always worry whether she's{nl}
getting along with friends...{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: Honestly, I can't{nl}
believe it! Her precious only{nl}
daughter's hospitalized, and{nl}
she won't even visit!{waitkey}I don't know how busy SEBEC{nl}
work keeps her, but she's a{nl}
failure as a mother!{waitkey}...Poor little Maki...{waitkey}{ret}
